WEBVTT

00:05:28.952 --> 00:05:31.904
Now imagine millions of sweat bees
choking the air around you,

00:05:31.928 --> 00:05:33.165
flesh-eating bacteria,

00:05:33.189 --> 00:05:36.579
the constant threat
of a landmine going off

00:05:36.603 --> 00:05:38.935
or an unseen hippo capsizing your mokoro.

00:05:38.959 --> 00:05:41.873
These are the scenes
moments after a hippo did just that --

00:05:41.897 --> 00:05:44.177
thrusting its tusks
through the hull of my boat.

00:05:44.201 --> 00:05:45.886
You can see the two holes --

00:05:45.910 --> 00:05:47.992
puncture wounds in the base of the hull --

00:05:48.016 --> 00:05:49.740
absolutely terrifying

00:05:49.764 --> 00:05:51.910
and completely my fault.

00:05:51.934 --> 00:05:53.297
(Laughter)

00:05:53.321 --> 00:05:55.404
Many, many portages,

00:05:55.428 --> 00:05:59.130
tree blockages
and capsizes in rocky rapids.